title: Fees; disposition
context: [ยง448B-9] Fees; disposition. (a) Application, examination, reexamination, license, renewal, late renewal penalty fees, inactive, and other reasonable and necessary fees relating to administration of this chapter, none of which are refundable, shall be as provided in rules adopted by the director pursuant to chapter 91. (b) Fees assessed shall defray all costs to be incurred by the director to support the operation of the dietitian licensure program. [L 2000, c 280, pt of ยง2]
